hosphate)." Fleet, CB  (2007):[4] "Product Information. Visicol (sodium acid phophate-sodium phosphate)." Salix Pharmaceuticals  (2007):[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767363028);
