duct Information. Fleet Phospho Soda (sodium acid phophate-sodium phosphate)." Fleet, CB  (2007):[2] "Product Information. Visicol (sodium acid phophate-sodium phosphate)." Salix Pharmaceuticals  (2007):[3] FDA. Food and Drug Admnistration "Oral sodium phosphate products for bowel cleansing.  http://www.fda.gov/cder/drug/InfoSheets/HCP/OSP_solutionHCP.pdf"   (2007):', 1767363028);
